 by its\ndifferent components and in modeling the dust polarized emission, which is a\nlong-awaited input for studies of the polarized foregrounds for cosmic\nmicrowave background.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 21 Nov 2019 19:00:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 31 Mar 2020 12:51:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-08"}
