ply that a collective response\nexists in the most central p-Pb collisions. These collective behaviors are\ndominantly produced on the stage of the medium expansions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 22 Nov 2019 07:45:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 26 Nov 2019 11:07:45 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 21 Jan 2020 07:39:20 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 15 Apr 2020 14:17:16 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Mon, 31 Aug 2020 09:16:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-02"}
